太后擔心個電視節目執笠個代價仲大過俾佢繼續做落去喎。」<br />\n<br />\n「此話何解呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「你睇吓個公園，繼續做就54億，但係阿公子話執咗佢要成100億喎。」<br />\n<br />\n「哼，咁你就要叫太后自己諗吓究竟錢重要，定係我哋三萬個衙差重要啲喇。」<br />\n<br />\n「大帥息怒大帥息怒呀，太后唔係咁嘅意思呀。太后仲話好樂於接受大帥你嘅指正架，如果因此引起誤會，太后係表示歉意嘅。更何況果少少錢，三跑淨係填海超支都80億啦」<br />\n<br />\n「小豪子公公，呢句嘢邊個講架？」<br />\n<br />\n「應該係太后講，今次一定一定唔關啲外國名人事。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:53:16.000Z","msg":"歡迎收睇 驚~訊~<br />\n我係你地嘅主持人 Chong Yong Yi 忠勇毅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69d5979237c0ea10d305d2d9cb35492d813e256","tid":2024134,"uid":83558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"民間頭條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a494661e59e73b47c0981ada3fef104010fcf117","tid":2024134,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:21:00.000Z","msg":"編劇你做乜上黎劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdf3109da52d7a417d759050312d031bb1ae17c","tid":2024134,"uid":231922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"樓主有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af842cef3dd52d85d611dfc9d356c3e608909842","tid":2024134,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:24:15.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}